steps to run the project

1-create python virtual enviorment using this command (before runing command make sure you already install python).

    virtualenv virtualenvName

2-activate the python Enviroment using this command
    
    source virtualenv_name/bin/activate   
    
    for more information follow the link for python enviroment https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/python-virtual-environment/

3-after activating virtualenv, go to the project folder name BlogWebsite and run this command

    pip install -r requirements.txt 

(make sure you are in BlogWebsite folder where exist manage.py file)

4-and than run below command

    python manage.py runserver


5-IF ERROR if statficles not load properly run the following command

python manage.py collectstatic

6-Again run 
    python manage.py runserver


Thanks for reading user guide :) 
